Role of the admin
If you started the Loomio group you are the first administrator of the group.  You can make other people admins.  Admins have a special role in Loomio, and are usually the people responsible for introducing and helping people in your Loomio group.

Group Settings
As admin, it’s worth checking that the [Group Settings](https://help.loomio.com/en/user_manual/groups/settings/index.html?utm_campaign=onboard&utm_medium=email) are right for you.  Adding a photo or image for your group will help people arriving into the group feel at home.  Use the group description to say what you will use Loomio to do, and how you expect members to participate.

