Privacy and Permissions
Take particular note of your group [Privacy and Permissions](https://help.loomio.com/en/user_manual/groups/settings/index.html#privacy?utm_campaign=onboard&utm_medium=email). Loomio offers a range of options for the visibility of your group from Secret to Open.  Consider carefully what permissions you grant to group members - in new groups, large networks or communities you may want to restrict permissions to keep everyone safe.

